ges-2015/2015-location-and-accommodations/|publisher=The Bridges Organization|title=2015 Location and Accommodation|accessdate=July 15, 2015}}</ref> |- | 2016 || [[University of Jyväskylä]], Finland<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bridgesmathart.org/past-conferences/bridges-2016/|publisher=The Bridges Organization|title=The Bridges Organization – Bridges 2016 |accessdate=October 23, 2016}}</ref> |- | 2017 || [[University of Waterloo]], Canada<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bridgesmathart.org/bridges-2017/|publisher=The Bridges Organization|title=The Bridges Organization – Bridges 2017 |accessdate=October 23, 2016}}</ref> |}
